   <title outputclass="Heading 3">
      <ph props="autonumber">5135.015-70</ph> Special use allowances for research facilities acquired by educational institutions.</title>
   <conbody>
      <p outputclass="List1">(c)  The <ph rev="Revised October 1, 2024">HCA</ph> may approve special use allowances as described at DFARS 235.015-70(c).  See <ph rev="Revised October 1, 2024">
            <xref href="https://armyeitaas.sharepoint-mil.us/:x:/r/sites/ASA-ALT-PAM-PP/_layouts/15/Doc.aspx?sourcedoc=%7BF79B63A9-3ED0-4830-89D1-F162968200C4%7D&amp;file=AFARSGG.xlsx&amp;action=default&amp;mobileredirect=true"
                  format="html"
                  scope="external">Appendix GG</xref>
         </ph> for further delegation.</p>
      <p outputclass="List1">(d)(3)(ii)  The <ph rev="Revised October 1, 2024">HCA</ph> shall make the determination at DFARS 235.015-70(d)(3)(ii).  See <ph rev="Revised October 1, 2024">
            <xref href="https://armyeitaas.sharepoint-mil.us/:x:/r/sites/ASA-ALT-PAM-PP/_layouts/15/Doc.aspx?sourcedoc=%7BF79B63A9-3ED0-4830-89D1-F162968200C4%7D&amp;file=AFARSGG.xlsx&amp;action=default&amp;mobileredirect=true"
                  format="html"
                  scope="external">Appendix GG</xref>
         </ph> for further delegation.  </p>
